I have been renting for an extended stay and I feel so lucky to have had the opportunity to stay here. Old Saybrook is absolutely beautiful and has many spots to get great shoreline views. The house is walking distance to a private beach and resides in a quiet neighborhood, providing a peaceful and enjoyable environment. However, it is also just minutes from anything that you could need, such as lots of shopping and many restaurants. The convenience to everything makes the location ideal. The house itself is quaint and comes equipped with more than you could need! The house’s beachy theme makes you feel relaxed as soon as you walk in. There is plenty of seating and space both indoors and outdoors to enjoy. Janet has been extremely helpful and has been available for anything that I have needed. I would highly recommend this place to anyone looking for a nice getaway or a convenient, yet charming place to stay.<br>
